  <div id="home_loggedout">
    <div class= "jumbotron">
      <div class= "container">
        <% if notice %>
          <div class="alert alert-success">
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
            <%= notice %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
        <% if alert %>
          <div class="alert alert-danger">
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
            <%= alert %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
        <div class= "hero-title">
          <h1>Ask for something and get things done!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class= "hero-description">
          <h3>With faskyn you can simply and quickly assign a  task or ask for a favor.</h3>
        </div>
        <div class = "hero-button">
          <p><%= link_to "Get Started", new_user_registration_path , class: "btn btn-success btn-lg" %> or <%= link_to "Log In", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class = "details">
    <div class= "container">
      <div class = "row">
        <div class = "col-md-4">
          <div class="col-padding">
            <span class="glyphicon-stack">
              <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle glyphicon-stack-2x"></i>
              <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-phone-alt glyphicon-stack glyphicon-stack-1x"></i>
            </span>
            <h4>Get and stay in touch with your industry fellows</h4>
            <p>Make and maintain win-win connections with people who you make business together</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class = "col-md-4">
          <div class="col-padding">
            <span class="glyphicon-stack">
              <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle glyphicon-stack-2x"></i>
              <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user glyphicon-stack glyphicon-stack-1x"></i>
              </span>
            <h4>Ask a targeted favor or assign a task</h4>
            <p>Assign a task to your lawyer, VC or fellow startup, or ask for a targeted favor from guys who you think could help.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class = "col-md-4">
          <div class="col-padding">
            <span class="glyphicon-stack">
              <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle glyphicon-stack-2x"></i>
              <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok glyphicon-stack glyphicon-stack-1x"></i>
            </span>
            <h4>Return the favor or get assigned</h4>
            <p>Enjoy the quick results and get ready to be assigned or return the favor within your area of expertise.</p>
          </div>    
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="examples">
    <div class= "container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="col-padding">
            <p>"These guys look good at distribution, but they may need some help with coding. Let's get in touch with them."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="col-padding">
            <p>"Hey Joe, we'd like to consult with you about sales. In exchange we can help you make your front-end better."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="col-padding">
            <p>"Hey Kate, sounds good. Let's meet next Wednesday."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="col-padding">
            <p>"Our accountant hasn't sent over yet the latest copies."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="col-padding">
            <p>"Nancy, please send over the docs in 2 days."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="col-padding">
            <p>"Jack, it's done. Let me know if you need anything else."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="get-started">
    <div class="container">
      <h4>Time to speed up and get things done.
      <span><div class = "hero-button">
        <%= link_to "Get Started", new_user_registration_path , class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
      </div></span>
      </h4>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= render 'footer' %>


